</p></li><li id="LI_CA72A11EC2AC4C48863612B5463B3EEE" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the top cover. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-5336C61E-428B-4155-A159-4E02791CDD76" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not lean on the strip support. 
</p></note></li></ol></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_840C79ECCB334F8AA1075BBA0086BC39" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_0B417F2969424F2E8B3BB07815511E4C" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Small screwdriver or pliers. 
</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves : 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-DB340B14-87E5-4FDB-8108-245D16C84FF1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-02F369FE-CECC-43CA-94C4-E28BEC9A7EB0" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-79664799-2A70-496A-8257-D18E3666F4FC-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-79664799-2A70-496A-8257-D18E3666F4FC-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_2ED55A2BDE0B4458AC37B33FC1C7B7AA" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_B5424687F5CB4E4CADC5ABF3E101FBF3" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
