</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Slide the curing carriage to the right hand side. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-59CE5481-FE29-4314-B69E-FD7FC9E1D269" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-076C99E6-00B4-430F-8C74-876F1B9C61DC-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-076C99E6-00B4-430F-8C74-876F1B9C61DC-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the connector and remove the sensor. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Use the small screw driver or pliers to loosen the brackets of the sensor. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Squeeze the bracket or push inwards with the screwdriver. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the sensor. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-92820012-FADF-4F26-AB0B-31E5C44642BF" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6267E290-5617-4996-81A9-A9FC6A901017-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6267E290-5617-4996-81A9-A9FC6A901017-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_E3FC7EE10DDC46BA880F87671551C890" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
